    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the garlic is fragrant, wash your <strong>spinach</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>spinach</strong> to the pan with your <strong>ground paprika</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until wilted</p>",
