      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>conchiglie</strong> to the pan with your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>, <strong>soft cheese</strong>, <strong>half</strong> your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(save the rest for garnish!), <strong>sliced chicken </strong>and the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>sun-dried tomatoes</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 1 min further or until the sauce begins to stick to the pasta – this is your <strong>creamy sun-dried tomato chicken pasta</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if it's looking a little dry</p>",
